name: Christopher_Knight_Home_Black_Two_Door_One_Drawer_Cabinet
reviews: I ordered this needing something in my downstairs bathroom in which to keep bath towels, toiletries, and yard work clothes! It was VERY easy to put the feet on...the rest is done for you! It is pretty and works beautifully for what it is intended!!!!!
description: The classic Asian blocking pattern gives this cabinet the appearance of an eight-drawer chest. However, further inspection reveals more versatile storage. A single drawer tops a two-door cabinet with a middle shelf within.
